{
  "text": "All previous clinical reports on ROS1 alterations in lung cancer have, however, emphasized that ROS1-associated adenocarcinomas are merely restricted to lower clinical stage, female gender and to younger patients. ROS1 translocations have been reported in an age range from 25 to 77 years, and the mean age was even lower than in ALK-positive lung cancers [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
